### Experience Ladder Protocol
**Unit Progression:**
-	**Green**: Basic training, high casualty rate, easily panicked
-	Multiplier: 0.7x (penalties to accuracy, ammo discipline, recovery, timing)
-	Mistakes: Early throws, mis-heard orders, slow transitions, over-pursuit
  
-	**Trained**: Combat-tested, reliable core
-	Multiplier: 1.0x (baseline)
-	Mistakes: Occasional misinterpretation, normal reaction time
  
-	**Veteran**: Seasoned, excellent timing and discipline
-	Multiplier: 1.15x (bonuses to accuracy, ammo discipline, initiative, autonomy)
-	Mistakes: Rare; may attempt complex maneuvers
  
-	**Elite**: Expert warriors, instinctive response
-	Multiplier: 1.30x (maximum bonuses)
-	Autonomy: Can execute complex orders with minimal instruction
**Progression:**
-	Survivors gain experience through engagement
-	Consistent victories and good tactics accelerate progression
-	Catastrophic failures slow progression or cause demotion
